#### What is the expected behavior?
Displaying an useable accordion with expansion panels generated 
out of dynamic data fetched by a method in a *ngFor-loop

#### What is the current behavior?
fires method infinitely until process ran out of memory and freezes

#### What are the steps to reproduce?
https://stackblitz.com/edit/angular-material2-issue-esus4p

